            <li class="fragment"><strong>RecordCollector</strong> - Multi-source data ingestion & validation</li>
            <li class="fragment"><strong>PromptTemplateManager</strong> - AI prompt orchestration & templates</li>
            <li class="fragment"><strong>RequestReviewer</strong> - Pre-processing validation & approval</li>
            <li class="fragment"><strong>ResponseReviewer</strong> - AI output quality assurance</li>
            <li class="fragment"><strong>HighlightCollector</strong> - Key insight extraction & curation</li>
            <li class="fragment"><strong>InsightAssembler</strong> - Final synthesis & output generation</li>
