            <li class="fragment"><strong>Agent Parallelism</strong> - Multiple AI agents work simultaneously</li>
            <li class="fragment"><strong>Frozen Boundaries</strong> - Completed components are read-only</li>
            <li class="fragment"><strong>Contract-First</strong> - APIs defined before implementation</li>
